::Prowl/Firearm::

Prowl watches Iron Raptor avoid Shadow's attack. They needed to get to 
the meeting.

-Love, I told Kluster we'd be at the meeting soon,- he thinks to Iron 
Raptor, hoping that she'd finish this battle soon.

His wing-mounted orbs could feel a bot approaching from behind. It was 
a Maximal. Several seconds later, Firearm stops near Prowl, 
transforming into robot mode.

"Kluster sent me to help you guys out. Anyone need help or a lift 
back?"
